race.description: Bet365 Same Race Multi Maiden Plate
race.comment: Wide open with a host of capable looking first starters in the mix. BRINSON (1) has started once and was in the market and ran well, finishing fourth at Werribee. Wound up strongly after being beaten for speed and looks suited here by the extra ground. SWEET FARNAN (9) ran on well fresh to place then got beaten a furlong in heavy ground. Just forget that and give another chance with firmer footing. KIWI HARMONY (5) ran well at both starts in first campaign and returns on the back of a jump-out win. Doubt she will be a maiden long.  PRINCESS OF SOL (12) returns from a break after the one start. Made debut on the Ballarat synthetic over winter and was safely held before being tipped out again. Fitter for two jump-outs and expecting a better result.
